data.documents_details:
Job Holder:
  • 07 Months Valid Passport With Old Passport (If have)
  • Visiting card
  • No objection certificate (NOC)
  • Marriage certificate copy (if spouse name not mentioned in the passport)
  • Marriage certificate (if a married couple is traveling together) (Attested by a notary public)
  • NID or birth certificate (must) one photo copy
  • Salary certificate
  • Recent 2 copy photograph taken in last 3 months (white background only, photo size 35 mm X 45 mm, Matt paper).
  • Personal bank solvency certificate
  • Document of properties
  • Blue book photocopy of car if any
  • All documents of financial solvency, Like: FDR, Share, Bonds or Other savings, security deposit or cash investment
  • Pay slip documents
  • Bank statement minimum 6 month


Businessman:
  • 07 Months Valid Passport With Old Passport (If have)
  • Renewal trade license copy with notary public (English translated)
  • Visiting card
  • Marriage certificate copy (if spouse name not mentioned in the passport)
  • Memorandum for limited company form page XII (One photo copy)
  • Recent 2 copy photograph taken in last 3 months (white background only, photo size 35 mm X 45 mm, Matt paper).
  • Company letter head pad (two copy)
  • Personal solvency certificate
  • NID or birth certificate (must) one photo copy
  • Bank statement minimum 6 month


Student:

  • 07 Months Valid Passport With Old Passport (If have)
  • ID card (Student) one photocopy both sides
  • Recent color photograph (size 2x2, matt paper)
  • Leave letter from school or collage original copy
  • NID or birth certificate (must) one photo copy
  • Marriage certificate (if a married couple is traveling together) (Attested by a notary public)


Housewife:
  • 07 Months Valid Passport With Old Passport (If have)
  • Marriage certificate (if a married couple is travelling together) (Attested by a notary public)
  • Recent 2 copy photograph taken in last 3 months (white background only, photo size 35 mm X 45m, Matt paper)


Important Notes

Please contact the Visa department for Document processing after the payment. Visa rate may change without any prior notice
